[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | 2 | CRITICAL | Security | Step 6/Expected Results | No access control model for surgeon-identifiable performance data; creates discoverable litigation risk and lacks peer review protection guidance | Pseudonymize surgeon_id in search index; add role-based access control for surgeon-identified queries; note peer review protection requirements |
